(199, 2040, 'id', 'Belajar Dasar-Dasar Microsoft Word || Panduan Lengkap untuk Pemula', NULL, '<font color=\"#131313\" face=\"Roboto, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\">Apakah Anda baru mengenal Microsoft Word? Jangan khawatir, video tutorial ini akan membantu Anda memulai dengan mudah. Kami akan membahas semua fitur penting dan memberikan tips praktis untuk membuat dokumen yang efektif dan profesional. Dalam video ini juga, Anda akan belajar cara mengoptimalkan penggunaan Microsoft Word untuk kebutuhan pekerjaan atau sekolah. Kami akan membahas teknik-teknik dasar dan canggih untuk meningkatkan produktivitas Anda dan mempermudah pekerjaan Anda di Microsoft Word</span></font>'),
(200, 2041, 'id', 'The Game of Life and How to Play It', NULL, '<p>The Game of Life and How to Play It<br><br><a href=\"http://librivox.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 100, 255); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">LibriVox</a><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"> recording of The Game of Life and How to Play It by Florence Scovel Shinn. Read by Amy Conger.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Florence Scovel Shinn, an illustrator living in New York City, became a teacher of New Thought after a divorce. New Thought was a movement which holds the belief that individuals can create their own reality through intentional thoughts and prayer, much like the current Law of Attraction movement. The Game of Life and How to Play It is her first book, and is remarkable for being written by a woman and meant for a genteel female audience.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox </span><a href=\"https://librivox.org/the-game-of-life-and-how-to-play-it-by-florence-scovel-shinn/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 100, 255); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">catalog page</a><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"> for this recording.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit </span><a href=\"http://librivox.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(75, 100, 255); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">LibriVox.org</a><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 44, 44); font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">.</span></p>'),
